#. <section class="sutta" id="sn35.72"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn35.72:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 35"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 35"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.72:0.2"
msgid "7. Migajālavagga"
msgstr "7. With Migajāla"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn35.72:0.3"
msgid "72. Dutiyachaphassāyatanasutta"
msgstr "72. Six Fields of Contact (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.44"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.72:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Yo hi koci, bhikkhave, bhikkhu channaṃ phassāyatanānaṃ samudayañca "
"atthaṅgamañca assādañca ādīnavañca nissaraṇañca yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, anyone who doesn’t truly understand the six fields of contacts’ "
"origin, ending, gratification, drawback, and escape"

msgctxt "sn35.72:1.2"
msgid "Avusitaṃ tena brahmacariyaṃ, ārakā so imasmā dhammavinayā”ti."
msgstr ""
"has not completed the spiritual journey and is far from this teaching and "
"training.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.72:2.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, aññataro bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "When he said this, one of the mendicants said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "sn35.72:2.2"
msgid "“etthāhaṃ, bhante, anassasaṃ panassasaṃ."
msgstr "“Here, sir, I’m lost, truly lost."

msgctxt "sn35.72:2.3"
msgid ""
"Ahañhi, bhante, channaṃ phassāyatanānaṃ samudayañca atthaṅgamañca assādañca "
"ādīnavañca nissaraṇañca yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāmī”ti."
msgstr ""
"For I don’t truly understand the six fields of contacts’ origin, ending, "
"gratification, drawback, and escape.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.72:3.1"
msgid "“Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, bhikkhu, "
msgstr "“What do you think, mendicant? "

msgctxt "sn35.72:3.2"
msgid "cakkhuṃ ‘netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na meso attā’ti samanupassasī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"Do you regard the eye like this: ‘This is not mine, I am not this, this is "
"not my self’?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.72:4.1"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”."
msgstr "“Yes, sir.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.72:5.1"
msgid ""
"“Sādhu, bhikkhu, ettha ca te, bhikkhu, cakkhu ‘netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi na "
"meso attā’ti evametaṃ yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya sudiṭṭhaṃ bhavissati."
msgstr ""
"“Good, mendicant! And regarding the eye, you will truly see clearly with "
"right wisdom that: ‘This is not mine, I am not this, this is not my self.’"

msgctxt "sn35.72:5.2"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ te etaṃ paṭhamaṃ phassāyatanaṃ pahīnaṃ bhavissati āyatiṃ apunabbhavāya …"
" pe …."
msgstr ""
"In this way you will give up the first field of contact, so that there are "
"no more future lives."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.72:6.1"
msgid "“Jivhaṃ ‘netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na meso attā’ti samanupassasī”ti?"
msgstr "Do you regard the ear … nose … tongue … body …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.72:7.1"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.72:8.1"
msgid ""
"“Sādhu, bhikkhu, ettha ca te, bhikkhu, jivhā ‘netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi na "
"meso attā’ti evametaṃ yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya sudiṭṭhaṃ bhavissati. Evaṃ "
"te etaṃ catutthaṃ phassāyatanaṃ pahīnaṃ bhavissati āyatiṃ apunabbhavāya … pe "
"…."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.72:9.1"
msgid "“Manaṃ ‘netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na meso attā’ti samanupassasī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"Do you regard the mind like this: ‘This is not mine, I am not this, this is "
"not my self’?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.72:10.1"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”."
msgstr "“Yes, sir.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.72:11.1"
msgid ""
"“Sādhu, bhikkhu, ettha ca te, bhikkhu, mano ‘netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na "
"meso attā’ti evametaṃ yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya sudiṭṭhaṃ bhavissati."
msgstr ""
"“Good, mendicant! And regarding the mind, you will truly see clearly with "
"right wisdom that: ‘This is not mine, I am not this, this is not my self.’"

msgctxt "sn35.72:11.2"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ te etaṃ chaṭṭhaṃ phassāyatanaṃ pahīnaṃ bhavissati āyatiṃ "
"apunabbhavāyā”ti."
msgstr ""
"In this way you will give up the sixth field of contact, so that there are "
"no more future lives.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn35.72:11.3"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""
